        "header": "Totally unlimited broadband with no price rises guaranteed",
        "text": "<p>Our Fixed Low Price Fast Broadband is now only {{price | gbp}} a month and has unlimited usage meaning you can use as much internet as you want, on as many devices as you want. Unlike other providers who regularly raise prices mid-contract, we guarantee you will have no price rises for your whole contract length.</p>"
